{"id":"concepts/trading-cards-as-business","title":"Trading cards as business","type":"concepts","html":"<h1>Trading cards as business</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Yahir's fall-2020 <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/grants-pass-teen-era\">senior year</a> business thesis — sports cards as an investment-and-resale lane. Surfaced as <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-09-01-kobe-card-collection\">Kobe card inventory</a> (collecting), then <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-09-23-sports-cards-mentor-questions\">sports cards mentor questions</a> three weeks later (workshopping the model). Adjacent to but distinct from his <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-03-22-stock-watchlist-march\">equities watchlist</a> — same investment instinct applied to physical scarcity.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Source summaries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-09-01-kobe-card-collection\">2020 09 01 kobe card collection</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2020-09-23-sports-cards-mentor-questions\">2020 09 23 sports cards mentor questions</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/kobe-bryant\">kobe bryant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disruption\">disruption</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disconnected-from-outcome\">disconnected from outcome</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/grants-pass-teen-era\">grants pass teen era</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2019-08-24-bulk-pencils","label":"Bulk pencils — back-to-school garage-as-studio prep"},{"id":"summaries/2020-03-22-stock-watchlist-march","label":"COVID-crash stock watchlist (March 22, 2020)"},{"id":"concepts/disconnected-from-outcome","label":"Disconnected From the Ou